## Proposed Changes
- Fix TrackBar accessibility issue #2818 

Fix based off code in `NumericUpDown`:
```cs
public override string Name
{
    get => base.Name ?? SR.DefaultNumericUpDownAccessibleName;
    set => base.Name = value;
}
```

